abstract: Police investigate reported rape at home of University of Nebraska quarterback Tommy Armstrong Jr and receiver Jordan Westerkamp; other college football news noted.
lead_paragraph: The police in Lincoln, Neb., were investigating a report of a rape at the residence of quarterback Tommy Armstrong Jr. and receiver Jordan Westerkamp.
